description: Aunty Lynne’s has been roaming the streets of America’s Finest City since 2015, feeding and refreshing all the folks with their delicious food, cool drinks, and frozen desserts, always with a friendly smile. You can find a fine variety of fantastic fare at this festive truck: Organic Tropical Smoothies, including Acai, Goji, Mango, Peanut Butter, Matcha, and more. Beautiful Bubble Teas with the freshest flavors, like Taro, Honeydew, Melon, and Thai. Hawaiian-Style Shaved Ice with premium syrups (all high fructose corn syrup-free) complete with a scoop of delightful ice cream. And if you’re in the mood for food, you’re in luck because this truck also serves a succulent selection of Asian Fusion cuisine, including Teriyaki Beef, Chicken, and Salmon, Korean BBQ, just to name a few. A portion of the profits go towards local youth sports leagues, so be sure to try a tasty treat from Aunty Lynne’s - you’ll fit right in with the family and be a part of something neat.
name: Aunty Lynne
